  levelNumber: 16
  levelName: "Chich\xE9n Itz\xE1"
  location: "Yucat\xE1n, Mexico"
  levelDescription: "Where the serpent descends with the sun, Chich\xE9n Itz\xE1
    stands as a wonder of the Maya world.\n\nChich\xE9n Itz\xE1,  was one of the
    greatest Maya cities, thriving between 600\u20131200 AD. It was a political,
    religious, and economic center, famous for its monumental architecture. The most
    iconic structure is El Castillo (Temple of Kukulc\xE1n), a pyramid aligned with
    the equinox sun, creating the illusion of a serpent descending its steps. The
    site also features the Great Ballcourt, sacred cenotes used for offerings, and
    temples that reveal Maya knowledge of astronomy and ritual. Today, Chich\xE9n
    Itz\xE1 is a UNESCO World Heritage Site and one of the New Seven Wonders of the
    World."
